                    Current                  


Celebrity Series of Boston, Inc.

                    To present world-class performing artists who inspire and enrich our community. We believe in the power of excellence and innovation in the performing arts to enrich life experience, transform lives, and build better communities. We envision a community of Greater Boston where the performing arts are a valued, lifelong, shared experience - on stages, inschools, in homes - everywhere.                  




