                                                    BRIEF-Vertex issues positive results from three different triple drug combination cystic fibrosis trials
                                                


                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    4:09 PM ET 07/18/2017
                                                


Vertex Pharmaceuticals Inc (VRTX). * Vertex Pharmaceuticals Inc (VRTX) issues positive results from three different triple drug combination cystic fibrosis trials. * Vertex says all three triple combinations led to statistically significant improvement in lung function in studies. * Vertex says each combination included kalydeco and tezacaftor and a third experimental drug.

















