                                                    Reuters – 
                                                    4:02 PM ET 07/18/2017
                                                


Vertex Pharmaceuticals Inc (VRTX) on Tuesday said three different triple combinations of cystic fibrosis treatments significantly improved patient lung function in clinical trials, bolstering its goal of a therapy that could help up to 90 percent of patients with the life-shortening lung disease.

















